Closure Comment — Cohesity AHV 7-Day Delta Report

Built 7-day AHV report using completed runs only (no running jobs).
Tracks PG additions/removals and VM membership deltas per PG.
Ensures accuracy via latest completed run per day with fallback handling.
Validated against Helios data across clusters; outputs are consistent.

Testing: Completed (functional + edge cases verified).
Status: Ready for production use.
